 所独有。该代表表示，Meta“严肃”对待这个问题，并下架了违反其规则的列表。 Ebay 告诉 Engadget，它“非常严肃”地对待召回，并结合人工智能和调查人员来发现潜在的不安全列表。它希望与众议院委员会就这些问题进行合作。</p><p>此次调查正值亚马逊因其销售行为面临<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-will-reportedly-meet-with-the-ftc-ahead-of-potential-antitrust-lawsuit-190316632.html">潜在的反垄断诉讼</a>，并且加大力度审查科技巨头的行为之际。 Meta 还缩减了部分购物功能，包括关闭<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/facebook-live-shopping-ends-october-2022-202501693.html">Facebook</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/instagram-live-shopping-shutdown-205824247.html">Instagram</a>上的直播购物。这些关闭是为了削减成本，但也使该公司剩余的商业计划处于更加脆弱的境地。</p><p><strong>美国东部时间 8 月 22 日下午 5 点更新：</strong>我们用 Ebay 的声明更新了该报道。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/amazon-meta-and-others-face-scrutiny-for-allowing-sellers-to-list-recalled-products-202005944.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazon-meta-and-others-face-scrutiny-for-allowing-sellers-to-list-recalled-products-202005944.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 85b7eb3c-54ff-4305-a855-714710ca925e</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 22 Aug 2023 20:20:05 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692738057</ingested><modified> 2023-08-22T21:01:05+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="3780" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-07/f7522110-e6a1-11eb-bfff-edb16fd0a4d3" width="6720"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:c